{"tid":619381,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】清Game？遲D先啦 Day191 6/4","createTime":"2018-04-06T14:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T18:43:04.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5cfc07fde82cbb0285063dc4370775d47aebc739","tid":619381,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:48:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=v%2FFFyb0r89fiJAo8Co9bFv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=8e986229\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=v%2FFFyb0r89fiJAo8Co9bFv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=350308de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"58e4469f26a7f2721c28d5b10591290ef424d69a","tid":619381,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:49:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b81915078c4b265d0e76edc9b333df87281ab370","tid":619381,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:52:18.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df33b98a812f149d70ee50e24e0042a19bd2f86","tid":619381,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,